WEBVTT

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.500
Reception: Where are you from?

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.500
Minh: I'm from Ha Noi city.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.500
Reception: What degree are you studying?

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Minh: I'm studying Computer Science.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Reception: Focusing on AI?

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.500
Reception: So Minh, do you know why this job has a huge amount of payment?

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Minh: I don't know, why?

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:37.000
Reception: Because I will have to go to another country to work.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Reception: There is a rule here. Once you are in, it must be kept secret.

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:44.000
Reception: I will give you a chance, all you need is put down a deposit and your passport.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Reception: Do you agree to this job?